rem. Definitely !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660280/extras/c8d68d9e8bd72eacb1f720a957053ebb.avif?t=1764082769\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match-3 mechanics to battle NPCs, bosses, and monsters in the game. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny cutscenes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill upgrade mechanism will help you a lot in your adventure.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many relaxing music to listen to.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are bored with fighting in the game, you can participate in the mini-games that take place in the world of the game.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with live2D cute girls.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun at tavern ( there are cute girls who will serve you ).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660280/extras/7c97a2906d9e92b63f7692a9a4e15000.poster.avif?t=1764082769\" width=578 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660280/extras/7c97a2906d9e92b63f7692a9a4e15000.webm?t=1764082769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1660280/extras/7c97a2906d9e92b63f7692a9a4e15000.mp4?t=1764082769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each location in the game will have different events happening. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And ye